  "text": "Storm tracks are extracted from the ERA-Interim reanalysis (Dee et al., 2011) using the tracking algorithm of [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] . These reanalysis data may be considered a historical realisation of weather produced by a physical coupled model of the atmosphere and ocean. Actual observations are assimilated in the process to provide a data constrained best estimate of historical weather. [CITATION_3] [CITATION_4] ",
